# Note: data/ (raw, screen, clean) and figures/ are intentionally
# committed, NOT ignored. The data is small (a few MB total across the
# whole project) and the OSRS Wiki realtime API only ever exposes a
# rolling ~3-month window -- committing the exact data used is the only
# way the headline results (measured spreads, buy-limit feasibility,
# backtest numbers) stay reproducible from a fresh clone.